latestIgtvVideos.title: 5K Fam✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
From a really conscious girl who used to think 100 times before posting anything on IG to a carefree girl who doesn’t give a damn about anyone who judges her ,this journey has been amazing.
It requires a lot of time and effort to come up with an idea ,to execute that idea,to edit it and to search for captions and hashtags,but it takes just 5 secs to pass a judgement.
You guys look at me in my video ‘ bhai ye to bdia enjoy kar rahi hai’.Yes, i do enjoy but boht efforts lagte h bhai.
A lot of time and hard-work is required  to post content but the support i’ve got from you guys motivates me to always come up with something new.I know a lot of people have judged me, bitched about me but trust me idgaf to you all because i have a lot of gems who’ve supported me from day 1 .Trust me when you guys share my videos on your stories i feel so  blessed and overwhelmed.
This post is for all those people who’ve loved me throughout,motivated me and also who’ve given me honest feedbacks.
Thankyou guys this wouldn’t have been possible without y’all.ILOVEYOU❤️
We are a family of 5K🥰🥰🥰✨
Video edited by @sushobhit_singh_photography  @sushobhit.singh

latestIgtvVideos.title: Gal Karke🦋
Happy Mother’s Day!❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Every Mother’s Day we try to make our mother’s feel special.
Our ways may have been different till now but this time due to lockdown i decided to surprise my mother with something that she’ll love (obviously at home).
So i woke up before her,surprised her with a cup of tea and spent the whole day talking to her and pampering her,giving her attention(leaving my phone aside).
I wanted to give her salon like experience at home😂.
From past 3 years i was unable to spend this day with my mom because i live in Delhi but this time i feel blessed to spend this day with her.
I love you Mumma!❤️
Happy Mother’s Day to all the supermoms out there!✨
